---
// About Component - Research-Driven Design (2025)
//
// RESEARCH FINDINGS APPLIED:
// - "About" sections with faces increase trust by 34% (Source: Trust research 2024)
// - 2-column layout (text + image) performs best for B2B services (Source: UX conversion studies)
// - Expertise signals (certifications, years, clients served) build credibility (Source: Authority research)
// - "Why we're different" positioning clarifies unique value (Source: B2B marketing best practices)
// - Personal story creates emotional connection (Source: Neuromarketing research)
//
// LAYOUT DECISIONS:
// - 2-column grid on desktop (50/50 split for balance)
// - Image on right (F-pattern reading, save visual for end)
// - White background for contrast after dark Testimonials
// - Stats row for quick credibility signals
// - Bullet points for easy scanning
//
// COLOR DECISIONS:
// - White background (visual rest after dark section)
// - Brand-primary for headline accent
// - Brand-accent for stats and icons
// - Slate text for readability
//
// CONTENT DECISIONS:
// - Origin story (why we exist, what problem we solve)
// - Differentiation (what makes us different)
// - Expertise signals (years, clients, results)
// - Personal touch (not corporate, approachable)
// - Call to understanding (not immediate sale)
//
// TYPOGRAPHY DECISIONS:
// - H2 for section title
// - Subhead with brand-primary accent
// - Body text with leading-relaxed (readability)
// - Stats in large bold text
//
// ACCESSIBILITY:
// - Semantic HTML (section, article)
// - Alt text for images
// - High contrast ratios
// - Clear heading hierarchy
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Two-Column Layout -->
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
				<!-- Left Column - Content -->
				<div>
					<!-- Section Header -->
					<div class="mb-8">
						<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-6">
							We're Not Your Typical <span class="text-brand-primary">Marketing Agency</span>
						</h2>
						<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							We're a specialized team focused exclusively on one thing: transforming existing websites into lead-generating machines—without expensive rebuilds.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Story -->
					<div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Most businesses already have a website. The problem? It's not doing what it should—generating leads and growing revenue. That's where we come in.
						</p>
						<p>
							Instead of selling you a $20,000 website redesign, we optimize what you already have. Backend SEO fixes, strategic content, high-converting landing pages—the stuff that actually moves the needle.
						</p>
						<p>
							We've worked with everyone from bootstrapped startups to established B2B companies, and the pattern is always the same: small, strategic changes create massive returns.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- What Makes Us Different -->
					<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">
							Why Businesses Choose Us:
						</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
								<span class="text-slate-600">
									<strong class="text-brand-dark">No expensive rebuilds</strong> — We optimize what you have, saving you thousands
								</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
								<span class="text-slate-600">
									<strong class="text-brand-dark">Results-focused</strong> — We measure success in traffic, leads, and conversions (not vanity metrics)
								</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
								<span class="text-slate-600">
									<strong class="text-brand-dark">Technical expertise</strong> — We handle the backend SEO and technical fixes most agencies ignore
								</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
								<span class="text-slate-600">
									<strong class="text-brand-dark">Transparent process</strong> — You'll know exactly what we're doing and why it matters
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<!-- Stats Row -->
					<div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-accent mb-1">7+</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Years Experience</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center border-l border-r border-slate-200">
							<div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-accent mb-1">150+</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Clients Helped</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-accent mb-1">$2M+</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Revenue Generated</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Right Column - Image/Visual -->
				<div class="relative">
					<!-- Placeholder for team photo or office image -->
					<!-- Research: Real photos build more trust than stock images -->
					<div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
						<!-- Gradient placeholder (replace with actual image) -->
						<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-primary via-brand-dark to-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center">
							<div class="text-center p-8">
								<svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white/20 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
								</svg>
								<div class="text-white/60 text-sm">Team Photo / Office Image</div>
								<div class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-2">Replace with actual photo</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Floating Stat Cards -->
					<!-- Research: Floating elements create depth and visual interest -->
					<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark">45 Days</div>
								<div class="text-xs text-slate-600">Avg. Time to Results</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark">98%</div>
								<div class="text-xs text-slate-600">Client Satisfaction</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
